# Codeigniter Development Environment Anyware | CIDEVANY

The idea is making development onboarding easy and stable. You just need to install Docker nothing more.
Local Terminal will use docker not Host.

## Requirement 
1. Debian
2. Apache/SSL
3. PHP
4. NodeJS
 
## Mode
1. Local Anycontainer
2. Local/Codespace Devcontainer
3. Remote Gitpod

### 1. Local Anycontainer
The main problem to solve is working with limited internet. At least for building images.
Next time use will be locally. 

1. Build with empty workspace

2. 

### 2. Local/Codespace Devcontainer 

https://github.com/docker/awesome-compose/tree/master/apache-php


### 3. Remote Gitpod